Peace of mind when you need it most

Here at Personal Group, we've been supporting the working backbone of the UK since 1984, with affordable and simple insurance plans. We have three straightforward insurance plans which offer financial support should you need hospital treatment (Hospital Plan), recovery following hospitalisation or day surgery (Recovery Plan) and life cover should the worst happen (Death Benefit Plan). It's peace of mind at an affordable price, and it’s quick and simple to submit a claim.
